# Tests skipped on the macOS (Darwin) fast-test run.
# Lines starting with '#' are comments; blank lines are ignored (see ci/jobs/fast_test.py).
# Grouped by known reason where investigated; the rest are not yet triaged.

# Float parsing: on Apple arm64 'long double' == 'double', so the fast float parser cannot
# reproduce x86/glibc results and its leniency differs. Out of scope here (precise-as-default).
